In speaker verification tasks, Equal Error Rate (EER) and Detection Cost Function (DCF) are often used as performance metrics. The calculation process of these two methods is provided in evaluate.py.

在说话人验证任务中，常常采用等错误率（Equal Error Rate，EER）以及检测代价函数（Detection Cost Function，DCF）作为评价指标。在evaluate.py中提供了这两种方法的计算过程。
代码来自InterSpeech 2020 challenge   [Short-duration Speaker Verification,SDSV](https://github.com/SdSVC/sdsvc.github.io/tree/master/assets)




